---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<Layout title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
	<section class="relative bg-gradient-to-b from-[#CEF3F5] to-white pt-16">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
				<div class="text-center md:text-left">
					<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
						<span class="text-brand-red block mb-4">Don't raise kids to be great kids</span>
						<span class="text-brand-teal">Raise kids to be great adults!</span>
					</h1>
					<p class="text-gray-600 text-lg md:text-xl mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto md:mx-0">
						You need more than school + authoritative parenting.
						You need an online resource + engagement tools to guide you in your journey.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="relative max-w-lg mx-auto">
					<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#CEF3F5]/50 to-transparent rounded-2xl"></div>
					<img 
						src="/images/heroimage-kids-as-great-adults.jpg" 
						alt="Raising kids to be great adults" 
						class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full"
					/>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-24 bg-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
				<div class="order-2 md:order-1 relative max-w-lg mx-auto">
					<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#CEF3F5]/50 to-transparent rounded-2xl"></div>
					<img 
						src="/images/kid-to-businesswoman.webp" 
						alt="Journey from childhood to successful professional" 
						class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full"
					/>
				</div>
				<div class="order-1 md:order-2">
					<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
						<span class="text-brand-teal">Nurturing Dreams </span>
						<span class="text-brand-red">Into Reality</span>
					</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-6">
						Every child has unlimited potential. Our mission is to help parents and educators unlock that potential, guiding children on their journey from playful curiosity to professional success.
					</p>
					<p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">
						Through innovative learning approaches and practical life skills development, we're creating a foundation for tomorrow's leaders, innovators, and changemakers.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-[#CEF3F5]/30">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center text-brand-teal mb-16">
				Visionary Learning for Emerging Adults
			</h2>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-[#CEF3F5]">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-red mb-4">Empowerment</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600">
						We provide parents and youth with the tools and insights to navigate the complexities of modern life.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-[#CEF3F5]">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-red mb-4">Innovation</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600">
						Through unique educational resources, we foster skills, responsibility, and a lifelong love for learning.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-[#CEF3F5]">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-red mb-4">Connection</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600">
						Join a growing community of forward-thinking parents and educators committed to raising exemplary adults.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="text-center">
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-teal mb-4">Join Our Movement</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					Together, we can shape a brighter future. Dive into our resources, engage with our community, and start the journey of empowerment today.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-24 bg-white">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center text-brand-teal mb-6">
				Aiming to be Great Adults
			</h2>
			<p class="text-gray-600 text-lg text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
				In society, the definition of a <span class="font-semibold">"great adult"</span> can vary based on cultural, social, and personal values. However, there are several universally recognized qualities and attributes that are often associated with the concept of a great adult:
			</p>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-[#CEF3F5]">
					<div class="text-brand-teal text-2xl mb-4">ğŸ˜Š</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-red mb-4">Effective Communication Skills</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
						<li>- Capable of expressing thoughts clearly and respectfully.</li>
						<li>- Listens actively and communicates in a way that fosters understanding and collaboration.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-[#CEF3F5]">
					<div class="text-brand-teal text-2xl mb-4">ğŸ’</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-red mb-4">Responsibility and Reliability</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
						<li>- Takes ownership of their actions and decisions.</li>
						<li>- Reliable and dependable in both personal and professional contexts.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-[#CEF3F5]">
					<div class="text-brand-teal text-2xl mb-4">ğŸ’</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-red mb-4">Emotional Maturity</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
						<li>- Demonstrates emotional intelligence, including self-awareness, empathy, and the ability to regulate emotions.</li>
						<li>- Shows resilience in the face of challenges and the ability to cope with stress in healthy ways.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-[#CEF3F5]">
					<div class="text-brand-teal text-2xl mb-4">ğŸ’</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-red mb-4">Financial Stability and Management</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
						<li>- Understands the importance of financial responsibility.</li>
						<li>- Capable of managing personal finances, including budgeting, saving, and investing.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-[#CEF3F5]">
					<div class="text-brand-teal text-2xl mb-4">ğŸ¯</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-red mb-4">Professional Competence and Continuous Learning</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
						<li>- Maintains a healthy balance between work and personal life.</li>
						<li>- Prioritizes physical and mental health through a balanced lifestyle.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-[#CEF3F5]">
					<div class="text-brand-teal text-2xl mb-4">ğŸ¯</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-red mb-4">Leadership and Influence</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
						<li>- Actively contributes to the welfare of the community.</li>
						<li>- Demonstrates social responsibility and environmental awareness.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-[#CEF3F5]">
					<div class="text-brand-teal text-2xl mb-4">ğŸ’</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-red mb-4">Community Engagement and Social Responsibility</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
						<li>- Positively influences others, whether in a formal leadership role or through personal interactions.</li>
						<li>- Inspires and motivates others towards positive change.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-[#CEF3F5]">
					<div class="text-brand-teal text-2xl mb-4">ğŸ’–</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-red mb-4">Ethical and Moral Integrity</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
						<li>- Exhibits honesty, fairness, and integrity in interactions with others.</li>
						<li>- Adheres to ethical principles in various aspects of life.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-[#CEF3F5]">
					<div class="text-brand-teal text-2xl mb-4">ğŸ¯</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-red mb-4">Healthy Lifestyle and Self-Care</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
						<li>- Shows respect and consideration for the diversity of people and opinions.</li>
						<li>- Fosters inclusive and respectful environments.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="relative py-24">
		<div class="absolute inset-0">
			<img 
				src="/images/day-care-final-cta-image-background.jpg" 
				alt="Parent and child learning together" 
				class="w-full h-full object-cover"
			/>
			<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50"></div>
		</div>
		<div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center text-white">
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">
					Parents play a crucial role in nurturing<br/>
					and sustaining the children's curiosity
				</h2>
				<p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-12 leading-relaxed">
					Curiosity is one of the most valuable and innate characteristics of a child. It's the driving force behind learning and exploration and is fundamental to cognitive development. Curious children are more likely to ask questions, seek new experiences, and ultimately gain a deeper understanding of the world around them.
				</p>
				<p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-12 leading-relaxed">
					This natural inquisitiveness, when nurtured and guided, can lead to a lifelong love of learning and discovery. Encouraging a child's curiosity is crucial in helping them develop critical thinking skills, creativity, and a sense of wonder that enriches their entire learning process.
				</p>
				<a href="/about" class="inline-block bg-brand-teal text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-teal-dark transition font-semibold text-lg">
					Read More...
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
